# 📂 Dataset for HAR-TFCL

This project uses **wearable sensor data** combined with **biometric features** to enable personalized Human Activity Recognition (HAR).  

---

## 📌 Dataset Details
- **Sensors:** Accelerometer, Gyroscope  
- **Biometrics:** Age, Height, etc
- **Format:** CSV with timestamps, sensor readings, activity labels  
- **Preprocessing:** Noise removal, normalization, segmentation into fixed windows, feature fusion  
- **Train/Test Split:** 80% training, 20% testing  

---

## 🔒 Confidentiality
The original dataset used in this project is **restricted and cannot be shared** due to privacy constraints.  

---

## 🌍 Public Alternatives
To replicate experiments, you can use publicly available datasets such as:  
- [UCI HAR Dataset]  
- [WISDM Dataset] 
- [Kaggle HAR Datasets](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets)  
